  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis:benefits of inspiratory muscle strenght training with Respifit S decreases
      symptoms, disability or handicap of patients affected by COPD. The inspiratory fraction
      (inspiratory capacity IC/ total lung capacity TLC)may be functionally more representative
      than other traditional indices.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
